import React from 'react'
import {Box, Center, ChakraProvider, Container, Stack, Text} from '@chakra-ui/react'
import Feed from './Layout/Feed/Feed'

const Home = () => {
    return (
        <ChakraProvider>
            <Container maxW="100vw" h="100vh" bg="#15202B">
                
                    <Stack direction="row" spacing="16px">
                        <Box w="300px" h="100vh" bg="tomato"></Box>
                        <Feed />
                    </Stack>
               
            </Container>
        </ChakraProvider>
    )
}

export default Home
